WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Togglo' is a Workbench game played on a 7 by 7 tiles board,
where each tile has its own 'backing' tile. Any tile can have one
of the following colours: red, green, blue or yellow. You have to
'toggle' or pivot tiles in such a way that they make vertical or
horizontal alignments of at least 2 neighbouring tiles of the same
colour... the more tiles there are, the more points you make.

  Have fun!

